<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Admission Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        /* Inline CSS is safer for email clients */
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
        .header { text-align: center; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; padding-top: 20px; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; color: white; background: #28a745; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; }
        .info { margin: 15px 0; }
        .info-label { font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h2>Admission Confirmed</h2>
    </div>

    <p>Hi <strong>${studentname}</strong>,</p>
    <p>Congratulations! Your admission for the course <strong>${coursename}</strong> has been confirmed on <strong>${date}</strong>.</p>

    <div class="info">
        <p><span class="info-label">Application ID:</span> ${applicationId}</p>
        <p><span class="info-label">Course Name:</span> ${coursename}</p>
        <p><span class="info-label">Date of Confirmation:</span> ${date}</p>
    </div>

    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:${contactEmail}">${contactEmail}</a>.</p>

    <p>Thank you for choosing our institute!</p>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>© ${year} Your Institute Name. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
